    "raw": "<!-- wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n[section bg_color=\"rgb(243, 243, 243)\" padding=\"60px\"]\n\n[row style=\"collapse\"]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.7\" text_align=\"center\" text_color=\"rgb(19, 19, 19)\"]\n\n<h2>Newcastlehub Services</h2>\n[/ux_text]\n[ux_text text_align=\"center\" text_color=\"rgb(41, 41, 41)\"]\n\n<p>Elevating Brands through Exceptional Web Design and Strategic Marketing. In today's digital landscape, a compelling online presence is essential for success, and that's where we come in. Our web design and marketing services work in tandem to create a holistic strategy that not only captures attention but drives results.</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[gap]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image_box img=\"413\" image_overlay=\"rgba(255, 211, 39, 0.558)\" image_hover=\"overlay-add\" text_padding=\"0px 0px 0px 0px\" class=\"service_box\"]\n\n[button text=\"Website Service\" size=\"large\" padding=\"15px 0px 15px 0px\" expand=\"true\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\" link=\"https://newcastlehub.info/website-service/\"]\n\n\n[/ux_image_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image_box img=\"432\" image_overlay=\"rgba(255, 211, 39, 0.558)\" image_hover=\"overlay-add\" text_padding=\"0px 0px 0px 0px\" class=\"service_box\"]\n\n[button text=\"Web Hosting Service\" size=\"large\" padding=\"15px 0px 15px 0px\" expand=\"true\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\" link=\"https://newcastlehub.info/hosting-plan/\"]\n\n\n[/ux_image_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image_box img=\"405\" image_overlay=\"rgba(255, 211, 39, 0.558)\" image_hover=\"overlay-add\" text_padding=\"0px 0px 0px 0px\" class=\"service_box\"]\n\n[button text=\"Marketing Service\" size=\"large\" padding=\"15px 0px 15px 0px\" expand=\"true\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\" link=\"https://newcastlehub.info/marketing-service/\"]\n\n\n[/ux_image_box]\n[ux_image_box img=\"658\" image_overlay=\"rgba(255, 211, 39, 0.558)\" image_h